OL,7,FCounting butterflies reduces anxiety
OL,8,Faccording to a wildlife charity based
OL,9,Fin Dorset.
OL,11,FButterfly Conservation surveyed people
OL,12,Ftaking part in the Big Butterfly Count
OL,13,Fand found it reduced anxiety by 9%.
OL,15,FResearchers also found that 15 minutes
OL,16,Fobserving and counting boosted
OL,17,Fparticipants' feeling of connectedness
OL,18,Fwith nature and mental wellbeing.
