OL,7,FDr Richard Fox, Head of Science at
OL,8,FButterfly Conservation, says: "While
OL,9,Fwe have long known that there is a
OL,10,Flink between nature and human
OL,11,Fwellbeing, this study is the first to
OL,12,Fprove that the simple act of looking
OL,13,Ffor and counting butterflies leads to
OL,14,Fa measurable decrease in anxiety.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/9
