OL,7,F"The results suggest that citizen
OL,8,Fscience projects such as the Big
OL,9,FButterfly Count can play a part in
OL,10,Fimproving people's mental health, as
OL,11,Fwell as gathering important data on
OL,12,Fhow butterflies are faring to inform
OL,13,Four conservation work."
