OL,5,Ccharity
OL,7,FDr Carly Butler, a Researcher in
OL,8,FNature Connectedness at the University
OL,9,Fof Derby and lead researcher on the
OL,10,Fstudy, says: "Our study showed that
OL,11,Feven small periods of time spent
OL,12,Fwatching and counting butterflies are
OL,13,Fbeneficial, with the benefits of
OL,14,Freduced anxiety and stronger nature
OL,15,Fconnectedness being the same whether
OL,16,Fpeople carried out just one 15-minute
OL,17,Fcount or took part multiple times.
