OL,7,FDr Carly Butler added: "Interestingly,
OL,8,Fthe more intensely participants felt
OL,9,Fthese emotions, the more their feeling
OL,10,Fof closeness to nature and noticing
OL,11,Fwildlife increased afterwards, with
OL,12,Fparticipants reporting they felt
OL,13,Fmotivated to help butterflies and
OL,14,Fnature more, by doing things such as
OL,15,Ftransforming their gardens into
OL,16,Fbutterfly-friendly havens."
