OL,5,Ccharity
OL,7,FDr Richard Fox says: "In order to save
OL,8,Fwildlife and ensure nature's recovery
OL,9,Fwe need people to care, and we know
OL,10,Fthat being connected to nature sparks
OL,11,Fthese caring feelings and a desire to
OL,12,Fdo something positive.
OL,14,F"This study indisputably shows that
OL,15,Fcitizen science activities, such as
OL,16,Fspending just a few minutes counting
OL,17,Fbutterflies, makes people feel more
OL,18,Fconnected to nature ` a vital step in
OL,19,Fthe battle to save wildlife.
