OL,7,F"We're at a tipping point, nature is
OL,8,Fin crisis, but we can all do something
OL,9,Fto help.
OL,11,F"Simple acts such as creating wild
OL,12,Fspaces to provide a haven for
OL,13,Fwildlife, or planting butterfly
OL,14,Ffriendly plants in pots on a patio,
OL,15,Fterrace or balcony can have a positive
OL,16,Fimpact."
OL,18,FThis year's Big Butterfly Count will
OL,19,Ftake place from Friday 12 July to
OL,20,FSunday 4 August.
